      "name": "Imagetic Disappropriation",
      "alternateName": [
        "Desapropriação Imagética",
        "Image Disappropriation"
      ],
      "description": "Artistic operation that displaces an image from its symbolic origin to establish autonomous signification, distinct from appropriation art through symbolic autonomy rather than appropriation.",
